<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.11">
<l>kuḻaliruṇ ṭucuruṇ ṭēṟiya kuñcik</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvinta ṉuṭaiya kōmaḷa vāyil</l>
<l>kuḻalmuḻaiñ cukaḷi ṉūṭuku miḻttuk</l>
<l rend="indent">koḻitteḻun tavamu tappuṉal taṉṉai</l>
<l>kuḻalmuḻa vamviḷam pumputu vaikkōṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">viṭṭucit taṉvirit tatamiḻ vallār</l>
<l>kuḻalai veṉṟakuḷir vāyiṉa rākic</l>
<l rend="indent">cātukōṭ ṭiyuḷkoḷ ḷappaṭu vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the Tamil [verses] expounded by Viṭṭucittaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">king of Putuvai, where flutes and drums resound,</l>
<l>About the flood of nectar that bubbles and rises to the suface</l>
<l rend="indent">from the holes of the flute on the beautiful lips of Govinda,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a hairknot where [his] black curly tresses abound,</l>
<l>[their] voices becoming pleasant like [his] flute,</l>
<l>they will be held in high regard in the assembly of the good folk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
